snippet.title: Take A Leak // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2351110/Take_A_Leak/

Navigate toilet puzzles, conserve pee, and follow the eccentric Mr. Latrine in Take a Leak. Choose to ascend to the Toilet Realm or explosively escape the facility. Your bladder, your choice!

Developed by
Dylan Quinton
